I JUST SAW JOANNA--

441
00:17:11.931 --> 00:17:13.097
                 I REMEMBER YOU.

442
00:17:13.165 --> 00:17:14.865
      I GAVE HER MY
     LAST $20 AND...

443
00:17:15.702 --> 00:17:17.968
I NEED THE OTHER $10 NOW.

444
00:17:18.037 --> 00:17:20.237
EXCUSE ME. I'M GONNA
 NEED THE OTHER $10.

445
00:17:20.306 --> 00:17:22.774
              IT'S $2.20 FOR
             NOW. FOR PARKING.

446
00:17:22.842 --> 00:17:23.874
                 AND THEN WHAT ?

447
00:17:23.943 --> 00:17:25.542
I ALREADY PAID HER
  IN THE GARAGE.

448
00:17:25.612 --> 00:17:26.877
     I PAID HER THE
    MONEY I OWE HER.

449
00:17:26.946 --> 00:17:27.945
 I GAVE HER $20.

450
00:17:28.014 --> 00:17:29.980
I OWED HER $3 AND
 I PAID HER $20.

451
00:17:30.049 --> 00:17:33.217
SO I NEED THE $10 BACK NOW.
BECAUSE I PAID HER THE $20.

452
00:17:33.285 --> 00:17:35.720
            THIS IS WHY I DON'T
           DO FAVORS FOR PEOPLE.

453
00:17:35.788 --> 00:17:36.721
BUT LISTEN. SIR.

454
00:17:36.789 --> 00:17:37.988
       ( horn honking )

455
00:17:38.625 --> 00:17:39.724
                PLEASE !

456
00:17:39.792 --> 00:17:41.225
   SIR. I'M AN
 HONEST PERSON.

457
00:17:41.293 --> 00:17:42.292
 I'M TELLING YOU--

458
00:17:42.361 --> 00:17:43.461
              I'M HONEST PERSON.

459
00:17:43.530 --> 00:17:44.461
                 REMEMBER THIS ?

460
00:17:44.530 --> 00:17:45.863
                YOU TOLD ME TO
              GIVE THIS TO HER ?

461
00:17:45.932 --> 00:17:47.097
                   THAT'S WHAT
                I'M GOING TO DO.

462
00:17:47.166 --> 00:17:48.899
            ALL I NEED FROM YOU
           IS $2.20 AND WE DONE.

463
00:17:48.968 --> 00:17:51.135
BUT I GAVE YOU THE MONEY. SO
 GIVE THE MONEY BACK TO ME.

464
00:17:51.203 --> 00:17:52.837
LET'S JUST PRETEND
IT NEVER HAPPENED.

465
00:17:52.905 --> 00:17:55.773
GO BACK AN HOUR AND PRETEND
 THIS NEVER HAPPENED. OK ?

466
00:17:55.842 --> 00:17:56.907
          JUST GO BACK AN HOUR ?

467
00:17:56.976 --> 00:17:58.743
    GO BACK AN HOUR.
PRETEND I NEVER CAME IN.

468
00:17:58.811 --> 00:18:00.311
              WHEN I DON'T WANT
             TO TAKE THE MONEY ?

469
00:18:00.379 --> 00:18:01.946
        AND YOU SAY. "TAKE MONEY
            TO GIVE TO HER" ?

470
00:18:02.014 --> 00:18:04.314
    AND I PROMISE YOU I GIVE HER
      MONEY. GO BACK TO THAT ?

471
00:18:04.383 --> 00:18:05.415
       I NEED...

472
00:18:05.484 --> 00:18:06.984
     EXCUSE ME. PLEASE !

473
00:18:07.053 --> 00:18:09.086
          HOW DO I KNOW NOW THAT
            YOU PAY HER MONEY ?

474
00:18:09.155 --> 00:18:10.587
 I'LL GET YOUR MONEY.

475
00:18:10.656 --> 00:18:11.756
           OH. YOU GET ME MONEY.

476
00:18:11.824 --> 00:18:13.490
            YOU KNOW. NEVER HAVE
             MONEY FOR PARKING.

477
00:18:13.560 --> 00:18:15.560
       YOU HAVE A BEAUTIFUL CAR.
       BUT NO MONEY FOR PARKING.

478
00:18:15.628 --> 00:18:18.262
    THIS IS THE SECOND TIME YOU
   DON'T HAVE MONEY FOR PARKING.

479
00:18:18.331 --> 00:18:20.965
               YOU THINK YOU CAN
                LOAN ME $2.20 ?

480
00:18:21.033 --> 00:18:23.734
                 HE'S JUST NOT
               GONNA LET ME OUT.

481
00:18:23.803 --> 00:18:25.670
          I'M JUST OUT OF MONEY.

482
00:18:28.475 --> 00:18:30.641
                  MAYBE MAKE IT
                 A 5. GREAT. OK.

483
00:18:30.710 --> 00:18:32.209
 LARRY. DON'T
 TOUCH MY CAR.

484
00:18:32.278 --> 00:18:33.410
             UH. YOU KNOW WHAT ?

485
00:18:33.479 --> 00:18:34.779
                  I'M GONNA GIVE
                   YOU BACK $10.

486
00:18:34.847 --> 00:18:36.380
                 I'LL MAKE IT
               WORTH YOUR WHILE.

487
00:18:36.448 --> 00:18:38.015
                 $10. I PROMISE.

488
00:18:38.084 --> 00:18:39.283
                      THANK YOU.

489
00:18:47.493 --> 00:18:48.759
 WHERE YOU BEEN ?
   YOU'RE LATE.

490
00:18:48.828 --> 00:18:50.728
          I HAD A PROBLEM IN
      THE GARAGE WITH THIS WOMAN

491
00:18:50.797 --> 00:18:52.697
         AND I DIDN'T HAVE MONEY
           TO PAY FOR PARKING.

492
00:18:52.765 --> 00:18:53.998
  IT'S ALWAYS
 THE PARKING.

493
00:18:54.066 --> 00:18:56.200
        I'M CONVINCED YOU DON'T
      WANT TO MEET DIANE KEATON.

494
00:18:56.268 --> 00:18:57.735
WELL. I'M HERE.
  AREN'T I ?

495
00:18:57.804 --> 00:18:59.670
            YOU'RE HERE. BUT
        YOU'RE A HALF HOUR LATE.

496
00:18:59.739 --> 00:19:01.538
         WHAT ARE YOU THINKING ?

497
00:19:04.210 --> 00:19:06.077
           THE GUY WOULDN'T GIVE
            ME BACK MY OWN $10.

498
00:19:06.145 --> 00:19:07.244
         HI. ARE YOU LARRY ?

499
00:19:07.313 --> 00:19:08.312
                            YES.

500
00:19:08.380 --> 00:19:09.980
         GREAT. DIANE'S BEEN
        WAITING. COME ON IN.

501
00:19:10.049 --> 00:19:11.248
                      THANK YOU.

502
00:19:11.317 --> 00:19:12.316
                HI. JEFF GREENE.

503
00:19:12.384 --> 00:19:14.151
                 HI. KIM. I'M
              DIANE'S ASSISTANT.

504
00:19:14.220 --> 00:19:15.485
           HI. NICE TO MEET YOU.

505
00:19:15.554 --> 00:19:17.288
            ( Diane )
      LARRY. IS THAT YOU ?

506
00:19:17.356 --> 00:19:19.690
   OH. HI. DIANE.
 I'M SORRY I'M LATE.

507
00:19:19.759 --> 00:19:21.926
          DON'T WORRY
        ABOUT IT. OK ?
      I'LL BE RIGHT DOWN.

508
00:19:21.994 --> 00:19:23.761
       MAKE YOURSELF AT
       HOME. ALL RIGHT ?

509
00:19:23.830 --> 00:19:26.163
        UM. YOU CAN TAKE A SEAT
       RIGHT OVER HERE AND WAIT.

510
00:19:26.232 --> 00:19:27.932
 OK. THANK YOU.

511
00:19:28.000 --> 00:19:30.334
          CAN I GET YOU ANYTHING
          TO DRINK. SOME COFFEE.
              WATER. JUICE ?

512
00:19:30.402 --> 00:19:31.601
 NO. THANK YOU.

513
00:19:31.670 --> 00:19:32.937
            I'M FINE. THANK YOU.

514
00:19:33.005 --> 00:19:34.805
                OK. JUST LET ME
              KNOW IF YOU NEED--

515
00:19:38.745 --> 00:19:40.344
       DID SHE HAVE AN ATTITUDE.
             THAT WOMAN ?

516
00:19:40.412 --> 00:19:41.545
                    OR IS IT MY
                   IMAGINATION ?

517
00:19:41.614 --> 00:19:43.613
    SHE HAD AN ATTITUDE.
          BIG TIME.

518
00:19:47.186 --> 00:19:48.886
WHAT ARE YOU LOOKING AT ?

519
00:19:48.955 --> 00:19:50.788
    THAT LAMP LOOKS
    VERY FAMILIAR.

520
00:19:52.892 --> 00:19:54.191
                      ( Diane )
                     THANK YOU !

521
00:19:54.260 --> 00:19:55.893
                    I'LL SEE YOU
                     IN A WEEK.

522
00:19:55.962 --> 00:19:57.995
             ( Carmen )
      OK. DIANE. I'LL CALL YOU
      WHEN I GET THE MATERIAL.

523
00:19:58.064 --> 00:19:59.129
                      BYE-BYE.

524
00:20:03.936 --> 00:20:05.269
                    OF COURSE...

525
00:20:05.337 --> 00:20:07.238
      WHEN SHE TOLD ME A "LARRY"
           KEPT HER WAITING.

526
00:20:07.306 --> 00:20:08.606
                 I SHOULD HAVE
               KNOWN IT WAS YOU.

527
00:20:08.675 --> 00:20:10.440
                LISTEN. YOU FIRE
                ME. THAT'S FINE.

528
00:20:10.509 --> 00:20:12.677
       YOU DON'T HAVE ANY TASTE.
      YOU DON'T WANT MY SERVICE.

529
00:20:12.745 --> 00:20:14.011
                    THAT'S FINE.

530
00:20:14.080 --> 00:20:16.046
        BUT YOU OWE ME A CHECK
       AND I EXPECT TO GET PAID.

531
00:20:16.115 --> 00:20:17.348
                   SO. I WANT
                THE CHECK TODAY.

532
00:20:17.416 --> 00:20:19.549
 OK. YOU SHOULD HAVE
 GOTTEN THE CHECK--

533
00:20:19.618 --> 00:20:21.451
                LARRY. I DON'T
              RECEIVE THE CHECK.

534
00:20:21.520 --> 00:20:24.254
       PLEASE. I AM A REASONABLE
          PERSON. I WANT YOU
         TO GIVE ME THE CHECK.

535
00:20:24.323 --> 00:20:25.856
MY BUSINESS MANAGER
 MAILED THE CHECK.

536
00:20:25.925 --> 00:20:26.924
           I WANT THE MONEY NOW.

537
00:20:26.993 --> 00:20:28.725
YOU WANT ME TO WRITE
 A CHECK RIGHT NOW ?

538
00:20:28.794 --> 00:20:31.628
          YOU FIRE ME ? I HAVE
        A REPUTATION. AND I HAVE
         A HISTORY WITH DIANE--

539
00:20:31.698 --> 00:20:33.097
WELL. I DON'T HAVE
  A CHECK ON ME.

540
00:20:33.165 --> 00:20:34.431
       QUIET DOWN.
       WILL YOU ?

541
00:20:34.500 --> 00:20:35.866
                LISTEN. YOU TELL
                ME TO BE QUIET ?

542
00:20:35.935 --> 00:20:37.134
       WILL YOU JUST
       QUIET DOWN ?

543
00:20:37.203 --> 00:20:38.768
             I WILL TELL DIANE
           NOT TO WORK WITH YOU.

544
00:20:38.837 --> 00:20:40.370
    WAIT A SECOND.
YOU'LL GET YOUR CHECK.

545
00:20:40.439 --> 00:20:42.339
          YOU LISTEN TO ME !
       DON'T TELL ME TO SHUT UP.

546
00:20:42.408 --> 00:20:44.041
 I DON'T CARRY
 CHECKS ON ME.

547
00:20:44.110 --> 00:20:45.276
 STOP THAT !

548
00:20:45.344 --> 00:20:47.044
              GIVE ME MY MONEY !

549
00:20:47.113 --> 00:20:48.045
                         LARRY !

550
00:20:48.114 --> 00:20:49.279
 HEY. STOP IT !

551
00:20:49.348 --> 00:20:50.347
                  DON'T. LARRY !

552
00:20:50.416 --> 00:20:51.748
      ( glass shattering )

553
00:20:51.818 --> 00:20:54.384
                    LARRY.
              YOU'RE AN ANIMAL !

554
00:20:54.453 --> 00:20:55.752
        ( both groaning )

555
00:20:55.822 --> 00:20:57.187
                      OH. LARRY.

556
00:21:02.328 --> 00:21:03.660
                 HI. DIANE.

557
00:21:30.222 --> 00:21:32.256
   EXCUSE ME. DO YOU
 HAVE CHANGE FOR $20 ?

558
00:21:32.324 --> 00:21:34.224
                          SORRY.

559
00:21:34.293 --> 00:21:36.193
   UH. DO YOU HAVE
 ANY CHANGE ON YOU ?

560
00:21:36.262 --> 00:21:37.461
 I NEED MONEY.

561
00:21:37.530 --> 00:21:38.562
    NO ?

562
00:21:38.630 --> 00:21:39.896
        DO YOU HAVE ANY
        CHANGE ON YOU ?

563
00:21:39.966 --> 00:21:41.031
   JUST A QUARTER ?

564
00:21:41.100 --> 00:21:42.900
     YOU CAN'T
 SPARE A QUARTER ?

565
00:21:55.581 --> 00:21:57.014
        HOLD THE ELEVATOR.
             PLEASE ?

566
00:22:39.158 --> 00:22:40.958
      ( heavy breathing )

567
00:22:43.729 --> 00:22:44.829
                   OH.

568
00:22:50.202 --> 00:22:51.801
                BAD FINGER.

569
00:23:00.512 --> 00:23:01.611
                             OH.

570
00:23:28.074 --> 00:23:29.473
                 HOW YOU DOING ?

571
00:23:31.244 --> 00:23:32.609
                     BAD FINGER.

572
00:23:34.146 --> 00:23:36.180
                  ♪ BAD FINGER ♪

573
00:23:37.283 --> 00:23:38.916
                ♪ HE'S THE MAN ♪

574
00:23:38.985 --> 00:23:42.586
                ♪ THE MAN WITH
               THE MIDAS TOUCH ♪

575
00:23:43.722 --> 00:23:45.889
♪ A SPIDER'S TOUCH ♪

576
00:23:45.957 --> 00:23:47.357
              MARISSA WINNAKER ?

577
00:23:47.426 --> 00:23:48.358
 YEAH.

578
00:23:48.427 --> 00:23:49.459
                   UH. WINOKUR ?

579
00:23:49.528 --> 00:23:50.694
                 DR. LYNCH IS
               READY TO SEE YOU.

580
00:23:50.762 --> 00:23:51.762
                         ROOM 8.

581
00:23:51.831 --> 00:23:53.230
 OH. THANKS.

582
00:23:54.633 --> 00:23:57.434
WHOA. I DON'T UNDERSTAND.
 WHAT'S GOING ON HERE ?

583
00:23:57.503 --> 00:23:59.770
  I CAME IN BEFORE HER.
 I SIGNED IN THE SHEET.

584
00:23:59.839 --> 00:24:02.706
   WELL. YOU'LL BE HAPPY TO KNOW
      THEY'VE CHANGED POLICY.

585
00:24:02.774 --> 00:24:04.374
 CHANGED POLICIES. WHAT ?

586
00:24:04.443 --> 00:24:06.577
             NOW WE SEE PEOPLE
              ON THE BASIS OF
          THEIR APPOINTMENT TIME

587
00:24:06.645 --> 00:24:08.345
     AND NOT THEIR ARRIVAL TIME.

588
00:24:08.414 --> 00:24:10.814
 BUT THAT'S RIDICULOUS.
  ONE PERSON COMPLAINS.
EVERYTHING GETS CHANGED ?

589
00:24:10.882 --> 00:24:12.649
          THIS WAS BASED ON YOUR
            IDEA THE OTHER DAY.

590
00:24:12.718 --> 00:24:14.318
   BUT WHAT ARE YOU
 LISTENING TO ME FOR ?

591
00:24:14.386 --> 00:24:15.886
     I DON'T KNOW WHAT
    I'M TALKING ABOUT.

592
00:24:15.955 --> 00:24:17.888
               SO IT'S NOT ABOUT
              THE POLICY AT ALL.

593
00:24:17.957 --> 00:24:19.790
             IT'S MORE JUST
         ABOUT YOU GOING FIRST ?

594
00:24:19.859 --> 00:24:21.158
       EXACTLY.

595
00:24:21.227 --> 00:24:23.360
         SO. IF YOU GO FIRST.
       WHATEVER POLICY THAT IS--

596
00:24:23.429 --> 00:24:26.263
THAT'S A GOOD POLICY. ME
FIRST. THAT'S THE POLICY.

597
00:24:26.332 --> 00:24:28.299
                 YOU KNOW WHAT
               WE'RE GONNA HAVE
               IN THIS OFFICE ?

598
00:24:28.367 --> 00:24:29.399
         THE "YOU FIRST" POLICY.

599
00:24:29.468 --> 00:24:30.500
 THANK YOU.

600
00:24:30.569 --> 00:24:31.568
                    DOES THAT
                MAKE YOU HAPPY ?

601
00:24:31.637 --> 00:24:33.203
 YES. THAT MAKES ME HAPPY.

602
00:24:33.272 --> 00:24:34.938
              GOOD. RIGHT AFTER
             TODAY. HAVE A SEAT.
              READ A MAGAZINE.

603
00:24:35.006 --> 00:24:37.107
               DOCTOR WILL BE
              WITH YOU IN A FEW
             MINUTES. THANK YOU.

604
00:24:43.749 --> 00:24:46.116
               ( Larry )
       SO. YOU KNOW THEY CHANGED
          THE POLICY. RIGHT ?

605
00:24:46.185 --> 00:24:49.053
              USED TO BE FIRST
             COME. FIRST SERVED.

606
00:24:49.121 --> 00:24:50.620
          NOW. IT'S APPOINTMENT.

607
00:24:50.689 --> 00:24:52.389
                    OH. REALLY ?

608
00:24:52.458 --> 00:24:54.458
             THAT'S FASCINATING.
             I DIDN'T KNOW THAT.

609
00:24:54.526 --> 00:24:56.126
              OH. NO. IT'S TRUE.

610
00:24:57.096 --> 00:25:00.764
            OH. CONGRATULATIONS.
                SHE EMERGES.

611
00:25:00.833 --> 00:25:03.200
     WHAT ARE YOU DOING IN THERE
       FOR 45 MINUTES ANYWAY ?

612
00:25:03.269 --> 00:25:04.668
             ARE YOU OK ?

613
00:25:13.545 --> 00:25:15.179
                  LASSIE MAVEN ?

614
00:25:16.848 --> 00:25:18.081
                      LASSIE ?

615
00:25:19.585 --> 00:25:20.617
                 HA. HA.

616
00:25:20.686 --> 00:25:22.051
                             OH.

617
00:25:22.120 --> 00:25:23.920
             OH. I'M SORRY.
            I DIDN'T REALIZE
         THAT WAS YOU. MR. DOFF.

618
00:25:23.989 --> 00:25:25.522
                 RIGHT THIS WAY.

619
00:25:28.194 --> 00:25:30.627
            DOCTOR WILL BE
         RIGHT IN TO SEE YOU.

620
00:25:37.670 --> 00:25:38.936
 HI. LARRY.

621
00:25:39.005 --> 00:25:40.070
                             HI.

622
00:25:40.139 --> 00:25:43.373
            SO--SO WHAT HAPPENED
               TO THE POLICY ?

623
00:25:43.442 --> 00:25:44.741
WE CHANGED THE POLICY

624
00:25:44.810 --> 00:25:46.810
 AFTER WE HAD THE DISCUSSION
AT THE BEGINNING OF THE WEEK.

625
00:25:46.878 --> 00:25:48.045
WE JUST CHANGED THE POLICY.

626
00:25:48.114 --> 00:25:49.145
                JUST LIKE THAT ?

627
00:25:49.215 --> 00:25:50.280
JUST LIKE THAT.

628
00:25:50.349 --> 00:25:51.548
M.D.: "MAKES DECISIONS."

629
00:25:51.617 --> 00:25:53.183
WHAT HAVE WE GOT ?

630
00:25:53.252 --> 00:25:55.385
THE FINGER. STILL
 BOTHERING YOU ?

631
00:25:55.454 --> 00:25:57.588
          MUCH. MUCH WORSE. MUCH
           WORSE. I GOT. I GOT--

632
00:25:57.656 --> 00:25:58.589
WHAT HAPPENED ?

633
00:25:58.657 --> 00:25:59.656
               I GOT IN A FIGHT.

634
00:25:59.725 --> 00:26:01.891
WASN'T THE FIRST INCIDENT
    A FIGHT AS WELL ?

635
00:26:01.960 --> 00:26:03.060
                    YOU BE VERY
                  CAREFUL THERE.

636
00:26:03.129 --> 00:26:04.261
   OK. THIS IS
 ANOTHER FIGHT ?

637
00:26:04.330 --> 00:26:05.495
                     YEAH. YEAH.

638
00:26:05.564 --> 00:26:07.030
  AND WHO.
SAME PERSON ?

639
00:26:07.098 --> 00:26:08.999
      NO. AN INTERIOR DECORATOR.

640
00:26:09.068 --> 00:26:10.934
   YOU'RE FIGHTING
INTERIOR DECORATORS ?

641
00:26:11.003 --> 00:26:13.637
                  AND I ALSO HAD
                  AN ALTERCATION

642
00:26:13.705 --> 00:26:16.340
             IN THE HALL WITH
           ONE OF YOUR PATIENTS.

643
00:26:16.408 --> 00:26:18.542
 WHEN'S THE NEXT FIGHT ?
MAYBE I'D LIKE TO SEE IT.

644
00:26:18.610 --> 00:26:19.643
                            AH !

645
00:26:19.711 --> 00:26:21.010
 VERY SORRY. AND
WHEN I DO THIS ?

646
00:26:21.079 --> 00:26:22.479
SAME THING. WORSE
WHEN I DO THIS ?

647
00:26:22.548 --> 00:26:23.480
                       YES. YES.

648
00:26:23.549 --> 00:26:25.249
   YOU HAVE
 FRACTURED IT.

649
00:26:25.317 --> 00:26:26.417
IT'S A HAIRLINE
   FRACTURE.

650
00:26:26.485 --> 00:26:28.185
  IT'S A SMALL ONE.
BUT IT IS FRACTURED.

651
00:26:28.254 --> 00:26:30.220
                        REALLY ?
MMM-HMM.

652
00:26:30.289 --> 00:26:32.789
                  SO. WHAT ARE
                  WE GONNA DO ?
                WHAT DO YOU DO ?

653
00:26:32.858 --> 00:26:35.359
WELL. I CAN'T DO ANYTHING.
      UH. RIGHT NOW.

654
00:26:35.427 --> 00:26:36.893
   I CAN'T DO
ANYTHING. LARRY.

655
00:26:36.962 --> 00:26:40.196
UNTIL YOU PAY MY WIFE'S FEE
  AND MY FEE. IN ADVANCE.

656
00:26:40.266 --> 00:26:43.700
   THAT'S THE WAY
WE'RE GONNA DO THIS.

657
00:26:43.769 --> 00:26:46.403
              LET ME TELL YOU
           SOMETHING. OK. JOHN ?

658
00:26:46.472 --> 00:26:48.472
              I DIDN'T ASK HER
            TO READ THAT SCRIPT.

659
00:26:48.540 --> 00:26:50.006
  SHE READ THE
 SCRIPT. LARRY.

660
00:26:50.075 --> 00:26:51.608
               SHE DIDN'T HAVE
            TO READ THAT SCRIPT.

661
00:26:51.677 --> 00:26:52.809
 SHE DID READ
  IT. THOUGH.

662
00:26:52.878 --> 00:26:54.210
                BUT WHO TOLD HER
                  TO READ IT ?

663
00:26:54.280 --> 00:26:56.012
   SHE READ IT AS
 A COURTESY TO YOU.
    AS A FRIEND.

664
00:26:56.082 --> 00:26:58.115
            THAT'S A COURTESY ?
           THAT'S SOME COURTESY.

665
00:26:58.184 --> 00:27:00.451
       I'D LIKE TO GET COURTESY
       LIKE THAT FROM EVERYBODY.

666
00:27:00.519 --> 00:27:01.951
                 BOY. I'LL BE
               IN THE POORHOUSE.

667
00:27:02.020 --> 00:27:03.553
 YOU'D BE LUCKY
   IF YOU DID.

668
00:27:03.622 --> 00:27:05.189
 SHE TOOK THE TIME
   FROM HER DAY.

669
00:27:05.257 --> 00:27:07.257
SHE MADE SOME SIGNIFICANT
  NOTES ON THAT SCRIPT.

670
00:27:07.326 --> 00:27:09.726
     WHO GIVES A SHIT ? I DIDN'T
    ASK HER TO READ THAT SCRIPT.

671
00:27:09.795 --> 00:27:13.096
      I DON'T WANT HER NOTES.
   I DON'T CARE ABOUT HER NOTES.
      I DON'T NEED HER NOTES.

672
00:27:13.164 --> 00:27:14.798
    DO YOU CARE
ABOUT THE FINGER ?

673
00:27:14.866 --> 00:27:17.434
 HERE'S WHAT'S GONNA
  HAPPEN WITH THAT.
    PAL OF MINE.

674
00:27:17.503 --> 00:27:19.169
HER MONEY UP-FRONT.
MY MONEY RIGHT NOW.

675
00:27:19.238 --> 00:27:20.337
  THEN WE LOOK
 AT THE FINGER.

676
00:27:20.406 --> 00:27:21.471
   HOW DO YOU
FEEL ABOUT THAT ?

677
00:27:21.540 --> 00:27:24.274
'CAUSE THAT'S THE GAME
  WE'RE PLAYING NOW.

678
00:27:24.343 --> 00:27:26.343
  WHAT. DO YOU NEED
A COUPLE OF MINUTES ?

679
00:27:26.412 --> 00:27:29.379
'CAUSE I GOT SOME PATIENTS
I COULD LOOK AT OUT THERE.

680
00:27:29.448 --> 00:27:31.615
   YOU KNOW WHAT ?
THIS IS EMBARRASSING.

681
00:27:31.684 --> 00:27:33.350
                YEAH. YOU SHOULD
                 BE EMBARRASSED.

682
00:27:33.419 --> 00:27:35.319
NOT EMBARRASSED FOR ME.

683
00:27:35.387 --> 00:27:36.920
ALL RIGHT. GIVE ME
 A COUPLE MINUTES.

684
00:27:36.988 --> 00:27:38.355
 I'LL BE BACK TO
FIX THAT FINGER.

685
00:27:38.424 --> 00:27:39.889
HEY. YOU'RE GONNA
   GET MILES.

686
00:28:44.389 --> 00:28:46.924
  Closed Captions conformed by
            SOFTITLER

